{"tid":2070324,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"木村哉哉«BG〜身辺警護人〜»第2季開播！搏命保鑣2 收視高開","createTime":"2020-06-19T05:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T16:56:17.000Z","uid":84018,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea3e12b348386edf7ab1c3cdee3632021fd1b9e","tid":2070324,"uid":84018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的，終於見到木村新劇開播，唔知有冇人鐘意木村拓哉既呢。<br />\n呢排追緊佢既系列日劇，有冇好介紹。<br />\n前排睇完 悠長假期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一季 Netflix有上架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二季<br />\n日本播出 隔日下晝 台灣KKTV/friDay影音有得睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S34R6a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS34R6a1.jpg&h=e408869a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg0NEsE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0NEsE.jpg&h=3d837d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">日劇天王木村拓哉扮演保鏢的朝日電視台劇集《BG~身邊警護人~》，相隔兩年再開拍第二季。劇集因疫情押後兩個月，終於在昨晚首播。首集在關東地區的平均收視有17%，打破上季首集收視15.7%記錄，全晚瞬間最高收視更達21.3%。</span></strong>男主角木村對收視成績十分滿意，今早亦在社交網留言，答謝觀眾支持。<br />\n<br />\n出道即巔峰 木村開IG <a href=\"https://instagram.com/takuya.kimura_tak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftakuya.kimura_tak&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=295f4be3\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/takuya.kimura_tak</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stb5raf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fstb5raf.jpg&h=8b8948e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgB1JWW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgB1JWW.jpg&h=b886f2b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid